Install first:
=================
sudo dnf install glade-devel-3.38.2-5.fc36.x86_64 (gtk + gst)
pip install mutagen (for metadata)


To install libhandy:
====================
git clone https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/libhandy/
sudo dnf install vala

Sometimes you need to run glade from the folder where you installed libhandy to see the Hand widgets
cd /path/to/the/libhandy
sh _build/run glade